data.meta_site_name: Grand Slam Professional Tennis Predictions and Picks by Nick Bollettieri. US Open, French Open, Wimbledon, Australian Open
data.text:
This morning at the IMG Bollettieri Tennis Academy two highly-ranked American juniors were practicing on court with veteran doubles standout Max Mirnyi. Jordan Cox, who just recently signed with IMG, is 17-years old and currently ranked #38 in the world in juniors. He is coming off of a successful summer where he reached the finals of Junior Wimbledon. He was joined by 18-year old Tenys Sandgren who just recently won the backdraw of the USA National Junior Championships in Kalamazoo. He is currently ranked #19 in the world in the juniors and he also reached the finals of the prestigious Easter Bowl back in April.
